----------------------------------------------------------- PRIMEIRA ----------------------------------------------------------
---- O Primeiro Outorgante é legítimo PROPRIETÁRIO e possuidor pacífico de um Prédio Urbano,
composto de rés do chão, primeiro e segundo andares, destinados a habitação, sito à Rua Arcebispo

(São Salvador) sob o Artigo 1591, descrito na Conservatória do Registo Predial de Ílhavo sob o N.º

---------------------------------------------------------------------AND -------------------------------------------------------------
SECOND PARTY: [redacted_name], married to [redacted_name] (NIF: [redacted_info]), born in
Marrif, Morocco, residing at [redacted_name] – No. 8 Ground Floor Left, City of [address] (Postal Code:
[redacted_info]), holder of Residence Permit No. [redacted_id], [redacted_id], issued by the SEF of Aveiro, Taxpayer No. [redacted_info], acting as TENANT;
----
HAVE ENTERED INTO THIS LEASE AGREEMENT, GOVERNED
BY THE CLAUSES AND CONDITIONS SET FORTH BELOW, TO WHICH BOTH PARTIES MUTUALLY
BIND THEMSELVES.  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
----------------------------------------------------------- FIRST----------------------------------------------------------
----The First Party is the lawful OWNER and peaceful possessor of an Urban Building,
consisting of a ground floor, first floor, and second floor, intended for habitation, located at Rua Arcebispo
Pereira Bilhano – No. 48, City of Ílhavo, registered in the urban property matrix of the Parish of Ílhavo
(São Salvador) under Article 1591, described in the Land Registry of Ílhavo under No. [redacted_info].
